## API Endpoints — All Tested ✅

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Result |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/health` | None | ✅ `{status: "ok"}` |
| `GET` | `/api/games` | None | ✅ Both games with all rank tiers |
| `GET` | `/api/lobbies` | None | ✅ 2 public lobbies with nested members |
| `GET` | `/api/lobbies/:code` | None | ✅ Full lobby with members |
| `GET` | `/api/lobbies/:code/messages` | None | ✅ Paginated chat history |
| `POST` | `/api/users` | None | ✅ Creates user, returns session token |
| `GET` | `/api/users/me` | ✅ Token | ✅ Returns current user |
| `POST` | `/api/lobbies` | ✅ Token | ✅ Creates lobby with auto-generated code |
| `POST` | `/api/lobbies/:code/join` | ✅ Token | ✅ Joins lobby, enforces rank filter |
| `POST` | `/api/lobbies/:code/leave` | ✅ Token | ✅ Leaves, host transfer if needed |
| `POST` | `/api/lobbies/:code/close` | ✅ Token | ✅ Host-only close |

### Key Behaviour Confirmed
- **Rank filter hard block** → BRONZE trying to join GOLD+ lobby gets `403` ✅
- **401 guard** → Unauthenticated POST to `/api/lobbies` returns `{"error":"Unauthorized"}` ✅
- **Lobby code auto-generated** → 6-char alphanumeric (e.g. `0U4B3W`) ✅
- **Host transfer on leave** → When host leaves, earliest member promoted ✅

---

## How to Run

```bash
cd server

# Start dev server (hot reload)
npm run dev

# Seed database
npm run seed

# Prisma studio
npm run db:studio
```

Server runs at: `http://localhost:3001`

